{"tid":1764272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方：譚皓文係西貢搵返","createTime":"2019-12-01T03:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T04:00:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c41a199485b7cbb6f49c0aeabbd93b9551a86840","tid":1764272,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:54:52.000Z","msg":"一名26歲男子譚皓文，於11月24日下午在馬鞍山鞍駿街親人家中露面後，不知所終，家人於11月27日向警方報案。事主身高約1.7米、體重約60公斤、瘦身材、黃皮膚、尖面及黑短髮，最後露面時身穿藍色長袖上衣、黑色長褲及黃色鞋。警方亦呼籲市民提供事主消息，案件交由港島總區失蹤人口調查組跟進。<br />\n親友心急如焚，分別在互聯網發文及多區貼出尋人啟事。至今日凌晨(12月1日)凌晨1時許，事主身處西貢蚺蛇坳。由於地點偏遠及地勢險要，消防到場協助搜救，至凌晨6時許，事主由救援船隻送往黃石碼頭上岸，由救護員初步驗查後，相信他並無大礙，但為安全起見，由救護車送院進一步檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191201/mobile/bkn-20191201081702397-1201_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191201%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191201081702397-1201_00822_001.html&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0By3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=4061c321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191201/mobile/bkn-20191201081702397-1201_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e5c3a52c586eed5fd6c4466af3f8abb27fe6c1ac","tid":1764272,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"出面d人<br />\n仲叫人唔好獅鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79b9ba7815df49ad0b88d53c62d034577b635b5","tid":1764272,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}